00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.800
 "This starts from the Great Emptiness and from the Great Emptiness arise the Great Compassion.

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:14.400
 It has no boundary, no restrictions, the pervasive compassion in every direction.

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:21.400
 That is started from your heart and with that from Great Emptiness and Great Compassion,

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:27.400
 you go there, then you become, or each of us becomes, Vajrasattvas.

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:32.400
 So the essence of Vajrasattva is Great Emptiness and Great Compassion, United Truth.

00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:36.400
 That is what the relief Vajrasattvas.

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:41.400
 And then also we see this visualization, all the different elements started.

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:46.400
 Where those elements come from? From the Great Compassion, Great Emptiness.

00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:54.400
 So this element is, all elements are, are wisdom, are compassion.

00:00:54.400 --> 00:01:00.400
 So that means everything what we see, gross level, is all started from the five elements.

00:01:00.400 --> 00:01:05.400
 So it is, this gross level, whatever it is, compassion, it is wisdom.

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:09.400
 Ourself is compassion, ourself is wisdom.

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:14.400
 We visualize that. That is our true nature, exactly as it is.

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:19.400
 Because we needed visualization of meditation, because of duality, interfering,

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:24.400
 for that reason, which is coming back to our home, sweet home, our reality,

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:28.400
 we need to have that, that concentration.

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:30.400
 So we meditate, that is what meditate.

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:33.400
 Otherwise, reality, nature is always with us.

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:36.400
 Our is nothing left, as Buddha said, in the teachings.

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:39.400
 All those great Muslims always said that.

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:44.400
 So now we visualize the Vajras in the tiny universe as the pure land of the Vajrasattva,

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:50.400
 as compassion and wisdom, and all the elements are the compassion and wisdom and emptiness.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:54.400
 Ourself as the wisdom and compassion and emptiness.

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:57.400
 And then we are going to recite a mantra.

00:01:57.400 --> 00:02:04.400
 And that is what, in this page 35, we look here, in page 35, the yoga of repetition.

00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:08.400
 That is what we are going to visualize in our heart center.

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:15.700
 Again as, our body is transcendental, verse to verse, and body of compassion and emptiness, or

00:02:15.700 --> 00:02:16.400
 wisdom.

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:17.400
 That is what it is.

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:23.400
 Inside there is also, in our heart center, transcendental, verse to verse, and body of emptiness

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:27.400
 and compassion, see Vajrasattva, exactly as in the teachings said,

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:31.400
 in this page 35, the yoga of repetitions.

