 Well, spreading the light that makes offering to all the noble ones.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:49.400
 That means the Buddhas and Bodhis to everyone.

00:02:49.400 --> 00:02:54.400
 And gathering their blessings, our blessings of every enlightenment,

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:57.400
 I invoke and observe to your heart center.

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:59.400
 You become embodiment of that.

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:03.400
 Or each of us become embodiment of that status.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:06.400
 And then the light again comes from your heart center,

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:08.400
 or the Vedya center, your heart center.

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:10.400
 And touch it with all the beings here.

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:13.400
 Purify the obscura, all the sentient beings.

