 Everyone's obscurations, obstacles, trouble, miserable condition, as I listed,

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:23.400
 and you know, we all know, we all in samsara, we know.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:26.400
 Everything is clear, we purify everything, really.

