 And then what they did, also what they did,

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:40.400
 establish them in the great bliss, one of the emptiness, two natural states.

00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:46.400
 And then light come back to your heart center, and now it's a circle.

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:50.400
 And then how we're going to recite this mantra here, see, in the teaching.

